com.qtplaf.library.util.list

Class IOList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qtplaf.library.util.list.IOList<E>

  • public class IOList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    A dual input/output list used to dispatch outputs from input. Normal usage would be a thread adding inputs and another periodically retrieving the output and processing it. Useful for queued tasks.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
